title: (Tues Full) Is Amy Overparenting By Charging Her Kids for This? + Bobby Feud: Top 10 TV Themes of All-Time + Not Good Update on Bobby’s Dental Drama

description:
Amy is charging her daughter for something to teach her a lesson…we want to know if it’s overparenting or not? In the Bobby Feud, can you name the Top 10 favorite TV Theme songs of all time? Bobby gave us a not so great update about his dentist visit yesterday.
